# nexuspred — environment variables (all optional)
# Copy to .env or export these before launching. .env is git-ignored.

# --- Tradovate accounts ---
# There are NO Tradovate credentials here. Each account is token-only and is
# configured in the dashboard under Settings -> Token Accounts (one access token
# per account). Tokens are auto-renewed via renewaccesstoken (access -> check
# token) and persisted to data/settings.json.

# --- Data directory (persist settings/tokens across deploys) ---
# NEXUSPRED_DATA_DIR=/var/data

# --- Dashboard HTTP Basic auth (protect a public deployment) ---
# DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=

# --- Server ---
# HOST=0.0.0.0
# PORT=9000

# --- Auto-updater branch (default: main) ---
# NEXUSPRED_BRANCH=main
